+.SH ""
+.PP
+The
+\fBgroupadd\fR
+command creates a new group account using the values specified on the command line plus the default values from the system\&. The new group will be entered into the system files as needed\&.
+.SH ""
+.PP
+\fBgroupadd\fR
+
+.PP
+\fB\-f\fR, \fB\-\-force\fR
