+.RS 4
+
+\fBcrypt\fR(3)
+
+.sp
+\fB\fR()
+.sp
+
+.RE
+.PP
+\fB\-r\fR, \fB\-\-system\fR
+.RS 4
+
+.sp
+The numeric identifiers of new system groups are chosen in the
+\fBSYS_GID_MIN\fR\-\fBSYS_GID_MAX\fR
