+.RS 4
+Apply changes in the
+\fICHROOT_DIR\fR
+directory and use the configuration files from the
+\fICHROOT_DIR\fR
+directory\&.
+.RE
+.SH ""
+.PP
+
+/etc/login\&.defs
+
+.PP
+\fBGID_MAX\fR (number), \fBGID_MIN\fR (number)
+.RS 4
+\fBuseradd\fR\fBgroupadd\fR
+
+\fBnewusers\fR
+ ID 
+.sp
+\fBGID_MIN\fR
+
+\fBGID_MAX\fR
+ 1000  60000
+.RE
+.PP
+\fBMAX_MEMBERS_PER_GROUP\fR (number)
+.RS 4
+
+/etc/group
+()( GID)
+.sp
+ 0
+.sp
+() NIS  1024 
+.sp
+ 25
+.sp
+( Shadow )
+.RE
+.PP
+\fBSYS_GID_MAX\fR (number), \fBSYS_GID_MIN\fR (number)
+.RS 4
+\fBuseradd\fR\fBgroupadd\fR
+
+\fBnewusers\fR
+ ID 
+.sp
+\fBSYS_GID_MIN\fR
+
+\fBSYS_GID_MAX\fR
